Recherche colocataire 
Bonjour je propose une colocation jeune sur fontenay sous bois, proche du boulevard de verdun et a  stations rer A et proches des commerces. 
Votre partie privée est composée d’1 chambre vide à meubler. Vous pourrez partager les pieces communes : la salle de bain( baignoire), la cuisine, les toilettes et le salon. L'appartement est orienté sud-est, votre chambre bénéficie du soleil l’après-midi.L'appartement dispose d'une cave et d'un ascenseur. Et il y a une petite colocatrice en plus, une adorable petite chienne.
Prix: € électricité + gaz + wifi (en moyenne).

user.description:
My name is Dana and I am an architect. I am quiet, and enjoy yoga, and meditation. I am looking for another girl to rent an apartment with in either Paris or Versailles. I’m planning to study soon for my masters in architecture. I am a very kind and sweet person, and love seeing other people’s faces. I prefer living with others than living alone, but do value alone, time and solitude. The ideal roommate for me would be a girl between the age of , who shares similar interests of either Architecture, art, or Yoga, who is clean and enjoys classy decorating with me. I don’t have many friends in France but I love to meet new people and cook for get togethers. I love animals but do not have any of my own at the moment. Let’s share some wine and cheese and make a space of joy together. Couples and boyfriends are welcome and I am happy to have guests. Let me know if I sound like a good roommate for you. 
Namaste 💗🙏
